                <list_item>
                    <paragraph>On the <inline classes="guilabel" rawtext=":guilabel:`Admin`">Admin</inline> tab, open the <inline classes="guilabel" rawtext=":guilabel:`System`">System</inline> tab
                        and click the <inline classes="guilabel" rawtext=":guilabel:`Shares`">Shares</inline> category.</paragraph>
                </list_item>
                <list_item>
                    <paragraph>Click the <inline classes="guilabel" rawtext=":guilabel:`Share Types`">Share Types</inline> tab, select the share type
